616
01:05:16,959 --> 01:05:19,249
<i>...aku mungkin bisa membunuhmu.</i>

617
01:05:19,249 --> 01:05:24,055
Hei! Hentikan! Hentikan, kau jalang!

618
01:05:25,362 --> 01:05:27,700
Dasar gila.

619
01:05:32,126 --> 01:05:34,700
